{"tid":1286000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求一個都不能少","createTime":"2019-07-04T17:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T18:21:46.000Z","uid":144541,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"969632c3afb5b1ef6bf3ba41c1d7991e9c8a21e4","tid":1286000,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:55:51.000Z","msg":"未正式「 撤回」惡法<br />\n未收回「暴動定性」<br />\n未成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n未停止檢控示威者<br />\n未有任何官員對今次事件問責<br />\n<br />\n政府一項訴求都唔願意回應，好意思叫人同你對話？<br />\n<br />\n我地每個市民已經好清楚表達我地訴求<br />\n<br />\n一萬人意見當耳邊風<br />\n十萬人遊行唔理<br />\n一百萬人示威就盲左<br />\n二百萬人訴求就hea回應<br />\n有人死左林鄭仲可以咁開心飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你當香港人係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>五大訴求一個都不能少</strong>"},{"pid":"a3603c4ad598ca377521db91621ed2e4d086578c","tid":1286000,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c1ba64084e29b6626bfe7eea2a1cfb9aee5ad85","tid":1286000,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3603c4ad598ca377521db91621ed2e4d086578c","tid":1286000,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:59:04.000Z","msg":"根本無野好傾，我地要講嘅已經講曬"},{"pid":"b57f240ded586c1ebc67612a1cdc7b7f7f9ff570","tid":1286000,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:59:44.000Z","msg":"唔止科大學生會，根本任何組織都唔應該代表整個運動去同林奠會面<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285818</a>"},{"pid":"50dc716e9e0f52035cb4ceb1dc7675f4fb55b0dd","tid":1286000,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:02:20.000Z","msg":"根本冇地方可以容納到同二百萬人見面，林鄭只有直接回應五大訴求<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285969</a>"},{"